Package: cli-uno-bridge
Architecture: %OOO_MONO_ARCHS%
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
 openoffice.orgVER-core (>> ${base-version}),
 ${cli:Depends}
Conflicts: libuno-cil
Provides: libuno-cil
Replaces: libuno-cil
Description: CLI binding for OpenOffice.org
 OpenOffice.org is a full-featured office productivity suite that provides
 a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains the CLI bindings to OpenOffice.org for
 accessing the OpenOffice.org API from Mono languages (e.g. C# and Boo)
 .
 Note that currently the use of Mono for add-ins & scripting inside
 OpenOffice.org is *not* yet supported.

Package: libuno-cli-basetypes1.0-cil
Architecture: all
Depends: ${cli:Depends}
Description: CLI-UNO bridge - base types
 OpenOffice.org is a full-featured office productivity suite that provides
 a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains cli_basetypes.dll, which, as the name implies, provides
 some base types.

Package: libuno-cli-types1.1-cil
Architecture: all
Depends: ${cli:Depends}
Description: CLI-UNO bridge - type library
 OpenOffice.org is a full-featured office productivity suite that provides
 a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains cli_types.dll, a CLI library which  provides classes
 and interfaces for components and client programs. It is a collection of
 all UNO interfaces currently used in the office.

Package: libuno-cli-cppuhelper1.0-cil
Architecture: all
Depends: ${cli:Depends}, cli-uno-bridge (= ${binary:Version})
Description: CLI-UNO Bridge - bootstrapping library
 OpenOffice.org is a full-featured office productivity suite that provides
 a near drop-in replacement for Microsoft(R) Office.
 .
 This package contains cli_cppuhelper.dll, a CLI library which provides
 bootstrapping code to bootstrap native UNO (use various UNO services
 implemented in different languages).

